quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  35,15,Aey logo! Tum Allah kay mohtaj ho aur Allah bey niyaz khoobiyon wala hai
  35,16,Agar woh chahaye to tum ko fana ker dey aur aik naee makhlooq peda ker day
  35,17,Aur yeh baat Allah ko kuch mushkil nahi
  35,18,Koi bhi bojh uthaney wala doosray ka bojh nahi uthaye ga agar koi giran baar doosray ko apna bojh uthaney kay liye bulaye ga to woh uss mein say kuch bhi na uthaye ga go qarabat daar hi ho. Tu sirf unhi ko aagah ker sakta hai jo ghaeebana tor per apnay rab say dartay hain aur namazon ki pabandi kertay hain aur jo bhi pak hojaye woh apnay hi nafay kay liye pak hoga. Lotna Allah hi ki taraf hai
  35,19,Aur andha aur aankhon wala barabar nahi
  35,20,Aur na tareeki aur roshni
  35,21,Aur na chaaon aur na dhoop
  35,22,Aur zinday aur murday barabar nahi hosaktay Allah Taalaa jiss ko chahata hai suna deta hai aur aap unn logo ko nahi suna saktay jo qabron mein hain
  35,23,Aap to sirf daraney walay hain
  35,24,Hum ney hi aap ko haq day ker khushkhabri sunaney wala aur darr sunaney wala bana ker bheja hai aur koi ummat aisi nahi hui jiss mein koi darr sunaney wala na guzra ho
  35,25,Aur agar yeh log aap ko jhutla den to jo log inn say pehlay ho guzray hain unhon ney bhi jhutlaya tha unn kay pass bhi unn kay payghumber moajjzay aur saheefay aur roshan kitaben ley ker aaye thay
  35,26,Phir mein ney unn kafiron ko pakar liya so mera azab kaisa hua